== Overview ==
The G33 lobs electro-magnetic grenades at targets which explode in a pulse of energy, disabling shield and reactor power within a short radius.

== Where to Acquire ==
The G33 Launcher can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
